        <rule id="5a16-dc0d-9786-221b" name="Repair Know-how" hidden="false">
          <description>If the Guildmaster starts the turn in contact with a damaged vehicle he may attempt to make a repair. If the vehicle is Immoblisied or has a Weapon Destroyed, one of these is repaired on a roll of 5+.</description>
