                  <description>If not guided this model must designate the closest friendly unit as it&apos;s primary target, then move it&apos;s full distance towards it in the movement phase, then in the shooting phase it must fire all its weapons at the closest enemy model to the friendly unit. If the friendly unit is locked in close combat, it must attempt to assault the enemy it is locked in combat with in the assault phase.</description>
