              <rules>
                <rule id="3814-d87d-c83e-c555" name="Deathblow" hidden="false">
                  <description>When a model with deathblow is killed while in close combat, if it has not yet fought this combat, place it on its side and it may make a single attack at the end of combat before combat result is calculated.</description>
